\ ----- code &2822..&283B -----
.sfx_explode
    \ Play 'explode' sound — two OSWORD &07 calls in sequence. Sound A (noise on ch 0) via params at
    \ &283B; sound B (tone on ch 1) via params at &2843. Note: amp.lo of sound A is at &283D = the
    \ byte that Loader3 PATCHES with `?&283D = 256 - V%` (the user's volume preference from
    \ options.BAS).
    STY scratch_28D3
    LDA #&07
    LDX #&3B
    LDY #&28
    JSR OSWORD
    LDA #&07
    LDX #&43
    LDY #&28
    JSR OSWORD
    LDY scratch_28D3
    RTS

